    "# DeepTruth — Phase 2: Build Hybrid Model Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "**Run this in Google Colab Pro (GPU runtime).**\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook defines and validates the full penta-stream hybrid model:\n",
    "- Stream 1: CLIP ViT-B/16 (semantic features)\n",
    "- Stream 2: EfficientNet-B4 (local texture)\n",
    "- Stream 3: FFT + Wavelet frequency analysis\n",
    "- Stream 4: SRM noise residual filters\n",
    "- Stream 5: Gram Matrix style features\n",
    "- Temporal Stream: Transformer across frames (video path)\n",
    "- Cross-attention fusion\n",
    "- Multi-task head: binary + manipulation type classification\n",
    "\n",
    "At the end of this notebook the model architecture is saved and ready for training."
   ]
  },
